  m_Name: Step7_Summary
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::EngineNarrationStep
  stepLabel: SUMMARY
  narrationText: "Now \u2014 let's watch everything work together.\n\nSix pistons
    stroke in sequence\u2026 connecting rods convert that motion\u2026 the crankshaft
    spins\u2026 the gear transfers power out of the system.\n\nFrom controlled force\u2026
    to continuous rotation. That is how a 6-cylinder engine works."
